<a name="howtorun"></a>
## 🚀 How to Run All Projects

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.9 or above
- pip (comes with Python)
- Internet connection (for first-time model downloads)

### One-time setup (install all dependencies)
```bash
pip install deep-translator nltk scikit-learn ultralytics opencv-python numpy
pip install mediapipe==0.10.9
```

### Run Task 1 — Language Translation
```bash
cd CodeAlpha_LanguageTranslation
python translator.py
```

### Run Task 2 — FAQ Chatbot
```bash
cd CodeAlpha_FAQChatbot
python chatbot.py
```

### Run Task 4 — Object Detection
```bash
cd CodeAlpha_ObjectDetection
python detector_v2.py
```

